 Bike Sales Dashboard, crafted using Excel's powerful features. This dashboard empowers you to analyze bike sales trends based on 
various filters, providing valuable insights into customer preferences and usage patterns.
With the help of pivot tables, you can effortlessly explore data based on Gender, Commute Distance, and Occupation. The intuitive interface 
allows you to filter and customize the view to focus on specific segments, helping you identify key market opportunities.
The centerpiece of the dashboard is the Trend Chart, a visually engaging representation of bike usage by age groups. This chart highlights
how different age demographics interact with our products, aiding in the development of targeted marketing strategies and product enhancements.
